data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home located in the heart of the Denver metro with NO HOA and on a culdesac.  As you enter the home you will find a spacious family room to your left with vaulted ceilings and grand windows that allow for lots of natural light.  Just past the family room you will find a large dining room with brick fireplace and a big open concept kitchen to include a center island, new appliances and a pantry.  You'll love the master bedroom that has its own private entrance to the covered patio, a large walk in closet and a private bath.  Down the hall you will find two more additional bedrooms the second bathroom and the laundry room.  The basement is the perfect rec room or 4th bedroom.  The backyard is a fantastic place to entertain or just enjoy the beautiful Colorado weather on the spacious covered patio.  This home is the perfect location only a few minutes from I-25, Park Meadows mall and all the shopping and restaurants you could want. This home is also in the highly sought after Cherry Creek School District.  Don't miss the chance to call this beauty home.
